  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Adventurer's Armory 2 pg. 9</em>, <em>Gnomes of Golarion pg. 22</em></p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\">Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 70 gp <strong>Weight</strong> 15 lbs.</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d8 (small), 1d10 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> x2; <strong>Range</strong> -; <strong>Type</strong> B; <strong>Special</strong> see text</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Two-Handed; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Hammers</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3><p>An alchemically fired piston in the head of this two-handed hammer strikes targets with astounding force. Successful sunder attacks made with a piston maul deal an additional 4 points of damage. A piston maul requires a thunderstone to function; otherwise, it functions as a greatclub. Inserting a thunderstone into the weapon's compartment is a standard action, and powers the weapon for 24 hours, after which the thunderstone is consumed.</p>",
